{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Styling IMSC documents","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Styling","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/\"><strong>IMSC</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details open=\"\">\n        <summary>IMSC guides</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Basics\">IMSC basics</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Using_the_imscJS_polyfill\">Using the imscJS polyfill</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Styling\">Styling IMSC documents</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Subtitle_placement\">Subtitle placement in IMSC</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Namespaces\">Namespaces in IMSC</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Timing_in_IMSC\">Timing in IMSC</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Mapping_video_time_codes_to_IMSC\">Mapping video time codes to IMSC</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/IMSC_and_other_standards\">IMSC and other standards</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>IMSC offers many options for styling documents, and most of the IMSC styling properties have direct CSS equivalents, making them familiar to web developers. In this guide you'll learn a bit more about IMSC styling including the difference between inline and referential styling, and efficient styling using inheritance and region styling.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"inline_styling","title":"Inline styling","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The simplest way of styling content elements like <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> is by specifying one or more style attributes, such as <code>tts:color</code>, on them. For instance, the following</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>textAlign</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>center<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>fontSize</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>64px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>red<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>fontFamily</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>proportionalSansSerif<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>fontStyle</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>italic<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n Hello, I am Mork from Ork\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>yields:</p><iframe width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mdn.github.io/imsc-examples/inline-styles/inline-styles.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"referential_styling","title":"Referential styling","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Inline styling is usually avoided since it generates duplication.</p>\n<p>Take for example the following two <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> elements, which have exactly the same style attributes:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   Hello, I am Mork from Ork.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    I come from another planet.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>In referential styling, styles are defined once and reused throughout the document — in a similar way to how CSS rules can be declared once and then applied to multiple HTML elements via for example, element or class selectors. In IMSC this is achieved by defining a <code>&lt;styling&gt;</code> element inside the document <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>, inside which is placed one or more <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> elements — each one of which defines a set of styles that you can reuse elsewhere. This is illustrated below:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tt</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>tts</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>styling</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>styling</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>I come from another planet.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Each <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> element is given an <code>id</code> (<code>\"s1\"</code> in this example):</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>which can then be referred to later in the document:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>this is equivalent to:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Hello, I am Mork from Ork\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>In other words, referencing a <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> element via its <code>id</code> and the <code>style</code> attribute is equivalent to copying the style properties of the <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> element onto the referencing element, as if the style properties had been specified using inline styling.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"style_inheritance","title":"Style inheritance","isH3":false,"content":"<p>If a style property is inheritable, like <code>tts:color</code>, then the style property will apply to all the descendants of an element it is specified on — again, this is similar to CSS and HTML. In the following example, the color <code>\"yellow\"</code> is applied to the text of both <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> elements because they are descendants of the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> element.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>I come from another planet.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Specifying a style on an element overrides any style specified on an ancestor, for example in the following snippet, the color of the second <code>&lt;p&gt;</code>'s text would be set to <code>\"aqua\"</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>aqua<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>I come from another planet.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"region_styling","title":"Region styling","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Region styling plays a special role in IMSC since a style property specified on a region is inherited by all elements that are selected to the region, starting with the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> element, as if the <code>&lt;region&gt;</code> element was the parent of the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> element. For example, in the following example, the text \"Hello, I am Mork from Ork\" will appear in yellow.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tt</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>tts</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>layout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>region</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>layout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">region</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"combining_styles","title":"Combining styles","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Referential styling can be applied to style elements themselves:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>styling</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>backgroundColor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xml:</span>id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">tts:</span>textAlign</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>styling</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Multiple styles can be also applied simultaneously on an element. For example, in the snippet below the style properties of both styles <code>s1</code> and <code>s2</code> are applied to the same <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> element.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>s1 s2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, I am Mork from Ork<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Inline styling","id":"inline_styling"},{"text":"Referential styling","id":"referential_styling"},{"text":"Style inheritance","id":"style_inheritance"},{"text":"Region styling","id":"region_styling"},{"text":"Combining styles","id":"combining_styles"}],"summary":"IMSC offers many options for styling documents, and most of the IMSC styling properties have direct CSS equivalents, making them familiar to web developers. In this guide you'll learn a bit more about IMSC styling including the difference between inline and referential styling, and efficient styling using inheritance and region styling.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-23T12:20:26.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/related/imsc/styling","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/related/imsc/styling/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/71f8c71a76731ecfc35f485719a363944a46a79d","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Related","title":"Web-related technologies"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC","title":"IMSC: subtitles and captioning for the Web"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Related/IMSC/Styling","title":"Styling IMSC documents"}],"pageTitle":"Styling IMSC documents - Web-related technologies | MDN","noIndexing":false}}